item.title: CVE-2020-5282|2024-08-04T08:22:09.078Z -- nick%20chan -- nickchanbot
item.description: In Nick Chan Bot before version 1.0.0-beta there is a vulnerability in the `npm` command which is part of this software package. This allows arbitrary shell execution,which can compromise the bot This is patched in version 1.0.0-beta
